<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reply-n">reply <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'plaɪ/    美 /rɪ'plaɪ/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-answer">1.★ <strong>回答；答复 (answer)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am looking forward to your early reply.
期待你早日答复。</p><footer>2008 福建书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make no reply</strong> 
不作答复</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-reply-to">in reply to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[正式用语] 为答复：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m writing <strong>in reply to</strong> your letter of June 1st. 
我写这封信是为了回复你6月1日的来信。</p></div></div>